LANGUAGE "SIC 1.0".
SCROLL STRONG summon_scroll
MODE CHANT.
PROFILE "CIVIL"


WORK MAIN WITH SIGIL UNUSED AS TEXT:
    SAY: "Entering MAIN.".
    LET SIGIL msg BE SUMMON WORK GREETING WITH SIGIL "World".
    THUS WE ANSWER WITH msg.
ENDWORK

WORK GREETING WITH SIGIL name AS TEXT:
    SAY: "Inside GREETING.".
    SEND BACK SIGIL name.
ENDWORK
